@startuml SPI_Top_FSM

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor LightGreen
    BorderColor DarkGreen
    FontSize 12
}

title SPI Top (spi_top) - Integration-Level Execution View

[*] --> RUN : rst deasserted

state RUN : Structural top-level wrapper\nNo internal state register\nSubmodules run concurrently

RUN --> RUN : route EEPROM request to eeprom_ctrl
RUN --> RUN : route MFRC request to mfrc_top
RUN --> RUN : shared bus arbitration in spi_arb

note right of RUN
  spi_top instantiates and wires:
  - eeprom_ctrl (Client A)
  - mfrc_top (Client B)
  - spi_arb (shared SPI bus)

  This module has no explicit FSM;
  behavior is continuous composition.
end note

@enduml
